# SDD Verification Report: memory-leaks-freezes

## 1. Overview
This report documents the verification phase for the `memory-leaks-freezes` change in the `splice-shell` project. It specifically audits and verifies the implementation of the temporary clipboard image sweeper, robust process tree teardown, async Tauri commands, PTY output throttling, and cleanup hooks across app startup, shutdown, session close, and PTY termination.

